 your service.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[testimonial image=\"126\" image_width=\"300\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Mr. Khai Tran\"]\n\n[ux_text text_color=\"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"]\n\nVery professional and great attention to details. Amazing response time. The personalized service is much appreciated in my case! Highly recommend it.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[testimonial image=\"126\" image_width=\"300\" pos=\"center\" name=\"Ali Raza\"]\n\n[ux_text text_color=\"rgb(0, 0, 0)\"]\n\nJohn is a tremendous individual with a passion to do the right thing. Having worked with him at EY, he has a heart of gold and would go above and beyond for his teammates and clients. I wish all the best with his future endeavors. Good luck.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '134-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-12-06 09:38:45', '2022-12-06 09:38:45', '', 134, 'http://localhost/luat/?p=137', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
